        <p>Dear <%= @charity.name%>,</p>
		<p>We hope this email finds you well. This is to confirm that your account with Give Hope has been successfully deleted upon your request. Your data has been permanently removed from our platform, and you will no longer receive any further communication from us.</p>
		<p>We want to take this opportunity to thank you for your time with us and for the incredible work you do towards empowering girls to live with dignity and confidence. We appreciate your efforts to create a better world for all.</p>
		<p>If by any chance, this was a mistake, please do not hesitate to reach out to us within 7 days of receiving this email, and we will do our best to assist you.</p>
		<p>We wish you all the best in your future endeavors.</p>

		<p>Sincerely,<br>The Give Hope Team</p>
